# Assets & Design Tokens

## Assets (single source of truth)

- Never hardcode asset paths like `'assets/icons/ic_lock.svg'` in UI code.
- Use:
  - `package:trip_marche/core/config/app_icons.dart` → `AppIcons.*`
  - `package:trip_marche/core/config/app_images.dart` → `AppImages.*`
- If a new asset is added, add a constant to the appropriate class and reference that constant everywhere.

## Colors & Typography

- Prefer `AppColors.*` and `AppTextStyles.*` over inline styles.
- If a color/style is used in multiple places, promote it to a token instead of duplicating values.

